  "industry_note": "UNS S43000 / EN 1.4016 / X6Cr17 / JIS SUS430 — ferritic stainless (Cr 16-18, C ≤ 0.12). Cold-worked (H/H2): σy 275-400. Tmax 815°C continuous (oxidation), 870°C intermittent. Automotive trim, kitchen appliance, dishwasher interior, deep-drawing (가공성은 304보다 우수)."
